entry.def: You use eventual to indicate that something happens or is the case at the end of a process or period of time.

example.ex: There are many who believe that civil war will be the eventual outcome of the racial tension in the country...
example.tran: 有很多人相信，该国种族关系的紧张最终将导致内战。

means.word_mean: 1. expected to follow in the indefinite future from causes already operating;
